    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふふーん！　どんなチョコを作ろうかなー\n猫ちゃんもいいけど、ワンちゃんも捨てがたいなー",
      "startTime": 6.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（よくよく考えれば、アイドルをつけるだなんて）\n（まるでストーカーみたいじゃないか……？）",
      "startTime": 13.7666668574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（いやいや！　これはマネージャーとしての責務！）\n（やましい気持ちなど一つもない……！）",
      "startTime": 19.333333524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "甘いのがいいって言ってたから、イチゴとか\n混ぜてみよっかなー？　他には……ん？",
      "startTime": 25.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（まずい、芽衣がこちらを振り返って……）\n（まさか気付かれたか！？）",
      "startTime": 33.250453024,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "……にゃーん",
      "startTime": 35.4993888217,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "猫の鳴き真似？　俺を猫だと思ってるのか？　よ、よし\nにゃ、にゃーん。あおーん。にゃあ～ん",
      "startTime": 44.133333524,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふっ。なぁんだ、猫ちゃんかー\n芽衣のことをこっそり見てるのかなー？",
      "startTime": 55.0712339878,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "次はそこのショッピングモールに行こうかなー\n猫ちゃんは入って来ちゃダメだよー？",
      "startTime": 61.9747454915,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "にゃ、にゃあ",
      "startTime": 64.5768942274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。買い物終わったら\n遊んであげるからねー。ばいばーい",
      "startTime": 69.233333524,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5926.64321689999,
          "startTime": 72.6666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……なんとかバレずに済んだな……\n割とギリギリだった気がするが……",
      "startTime": 77.335588403,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "しかしショッピングモールは人が多そうだな\n入れ違いになってもまずいしここで待つとしよう",
      "startTime": 83.3,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_zawa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 79.7308821953
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数十分後",
      "startTime": 87.6851679123,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "全然出て来ない。それだけ本気ということか……\nはぁ、俺は何をやっているんだろう",
      "startTime": 94.8999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の気持ちを止める権利なんて俺にはない\nだが、芽衣がアイドルを辞めるなんて、俺は……",
      "startTime": 102.1254442371,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4299.997967199999,
          "startTime": 102.9273221308
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あれ！？　{user}さんどうしたの！？\nぷるぷる震えて……お腹痛くなっちゃった！？",
      "startTime": 109.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "い、いや、なんでもないんだ、芽衣……\nって、芽衣！？　どうしてここに！？",
      "startTime": 116.066667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "何か変な物でも食べちゃった！？\n救急車呼んだ方がいいかな！？",
      "startTime": 120.9999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、ちが……と、とにかくここで騒ぐのはまずいな\nひとまず落ち着ける場所を探そう",
      "startTime": 127.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "なーんだ、じゃあ体調悪くなったんじゃないんだね？\n心配しちゃったよー",
      "startTime": 136.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "すまなかった、紛らわしい真似をして……\nしかし参ったな。まさか尾行がバレていたなんて",
      "startTime": 142.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、じーっと芽衣のこと\n見てたんだもん。すぐに分かったよー",
      "startTime": 149.666667366,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、猫ちゃんの声真似可愛かったなー\n凄く頑張ってたから気付かないフリしちゃった",
      "startTime": 157.7333309809,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱりあれもバレてたのか……\n誤魔化せていると思っていたんだが……",
      "startTime": 163.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "確かこんな感じだったっけ？\nにゃーん、あお～ん。にゃあ～ん",
      "startTime": 170.7999976475,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "恥ずかしいから掘り返さないでくれ……それより\nその袋の中身って、もしかしてチョコの材料か？",
      "startTime": 179.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_13_02-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよー。失敗した時のことも考えて\n予定よりも沢山買っちゃった～",
      "startTime": 188.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon"
    },
